sec.p:
We employ the triangular fuzzy number to estimate the CDC directors’ linguistic rating, which comprises lower, middle and upper bounds. Next, we sum up the rating and use the method of centroid defuzzification to provide a definite reference for a CDC head director who audits the final medical supplies’ dispensing amount. The formula of defuzzification is as follows:
